OL,3,CMan loses second bid to challenge
OL,4,Cappeal over his Manchester Arena hoax
OL,5,Ctheory
OL,7,FAn author has been denied a second
OL,8,Fchance to challenge a ruling that his
OL,9,Ftheory is "absurd and fantastical"
OL,10,Fafter claiming the Manchester Arena
OL,11,Fbombing was staged and did not kill
OL,12,Fanyone.
OL,14,FRichard Hall is being sued for
OL,15,Fharassment, misuse of private
OL,16,Finformation and data protection by
OL,17,Fbombing survivors Martin and Eve
OL,18,FHibbert at the High Court.
