OL,5,Ctheory
OL,7,FThe father and daughter suffered life-
OL,8,Fchanging injuries after attending the
OL,9,FAriana Grande concert in May 2017,
OL,10,Fwith Mr Hibbert left with a spinal
OL,11,Fcord injury and Miss Hibbert facing
OL,12,Fsevere brain damage.
OL,14,FHowever, Mr Hall has claimed that the
OL,15,Fattack, in which Salman Abedi
OL,16,Fdetonated a homemade rucksack bomb in
OL,17,Fthe crowd of concert-goers, was faked
OL,18,Fby government agencies.
