OL,5,Ctheory
OL,7,FMr Hibbert and his daughter were
OL,8,Fsuccessful in a bid for summary
OL,9,Fjudgment in a preliminary ruling in
OL,10,FFebruary, meaning a legal step to
OL,11,Fdecide parts of the case without a
OL,12,Ftrial on several parts of the case's
OL,13,Fbackground.
OL,15,FThis included rulings on whether the
OL,16,FHibberts' injuries were caused by the
OL,17,Fbombing and whether 22 people did die
OL,18,Fduring the attack.
