OL,3,CMan loses second bid to challenge
OL,4,Cappeal over his Manchester Arena hoax
OL,5,Ctheory
OL,7,FMr Hall lost an initial bid to appeal
OL,8,Fagainst the judgment without a hearing
OL,9,Fin March - he was denied again on 21
OL,10,FJune.
OL,12,FBarrister Paul Oakley, for Mr Hall,
OL,13,Fsaid that while a judge may find some
OL,14,Fof the allegations to be
OL,15,F"distasteful", the issues were too
OL,16,Fcomplicated to be dealt with through
OL,17,Fsummary judgement.
