OL,5,Ctheory
OL,7,FHe told the High Court in London: "I'm
OL,8,Fnot saying my client is going to prove
OL,9,Fhe is correct at trial, I am saying he
OL,10,Fis entitled to a fair trial."
OL,12,FWhen asked what Mr Hall's argument was
OL,13,Fabout where the 22 people who were
OL,14,Ffound to have died in the attack are
OL,15,Fnow, Mr Oakley said: "Three died
OL,16,Fearlier, others it appears are abroad."
OL,18,FMr Hall also said: "A funeral is not
OL,19,Fevidence of a death, it is evidence of
OL,20,Fa wooden box."
