OL,3,CMan loses second bid to challenge
OL,4,Cappeal over his Manchester Arena hoax
OL,5,Ctheory
OL,7,FIn written submissions, Mr Oakley
OL,8,Fclaimed Mr Hall wanted to bring an
OL,9,Fappeal due to the previous judge's
OL,10,F"comprehensive failure to address
OL,11,Ffactual and relevant evidence".
OL,13,FBut at the end of the hearing, Mr
OL,14,FJustice Julian Knowles dismissed Mr
OL,15,FHall's renewed bid to bring an appeal
OL,16,Fand said his full reasons would be
OL,17,Fprovided in writing.
